{"tid":688600,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林振強：關愛座HUNTER是我的偶像","createTime":"2018-06-03T11:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T02:16:25.000Z","uid":51469,"like":39,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdd917eb0ba4d1871733899c7cdbb0a8cf9a203","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"「關愛座HUNTER是我的偶像。<br />\n<br />\n「有些人，例如愛因斯坦，可以憑一己之力，改變世界，非常厲害。關愛座HUNTER改變不了世界，但他可以獨力改變一個討論的質素。<br />\n<br />\n「任何討論，只要見關愛座HUNTER有份出現，你就知道，這個討論必會變為低質、獵毛，和像孔乙己。以一人之力，左右一個討論，或一件論壇，這正是我渴望擁有的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n「最近，論壇的本土派討論，又見關愛座HUNTER。關愛座HUNTER日日罵著五毛的行徑，底下是一連串他口中的五毛挖出他過去表裏不一的瘡疤,一張張他真人玉照的改圖，有趣無比，登時令到嘲諷的氣溫激升，討論質素急降。據聞，事後還惹來他本人不少投訴。<br />\n<br />\n「但那又有甚麼所謂？當年，伽利略（Galelio）獨力改變世人對天文的概念，不也是被人投訴，甚至拉了去坐牢嗎？茄喱啡才沒有人投訴。 」<br />\n<br />\n下面......"},{"pid":"ca010e83224a4ba9e9dd9d6d0ecb908d5b826df7","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba509ccc5f6392fab2d9d79895c2f185d60f60aa","tid":688600,"uid":2436,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93e2466d8c657af302c7e978109ea4365c8ce511","tid":688600,"uid":57705,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1548de0b57f9e03a5ba8731468cde26a621a7bcd","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9f66e21d03aeeea771ae46010310f0b465c58b","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb1df4ac677860e03a3b149899f0088199e9527","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e61a1bb44f72a195d3cb98e4e6bdf5a8866a193","tid":688600,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"林振強唔係走咗咩？"},{"pid":"a4a1e0185da7ef3a6ec97605d696f66e49f8c3d5","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e61a1bb44f72a195d3cb98e4e6bdf5a8866a193","tid":688600,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"林振強唔係走咗咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走左好耐啦"},{"pid":"dba7774366259fedb1136287b8aef9f09b1dd819","tid":688600,"uid":123456,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/015141_926857a307104dcbbd5d1f1bf0ce191a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F015141_926857a307104dcbbd5d1f1bf0ce191a.gif&h=f58e9e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332eba8b298b1b7b50a060816dbc795ff5c4e1ff","tid":688600,"uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主五毛賈雨村抹黑本土派有功<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=211da708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1ad97502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bbe0f1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來大陸仔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132904_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132904_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=676cd829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0ce86f60fbb34b697520eb6471bb9fa07e89082c","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:59:17.000Z","msg":"黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beafc497e6e8c2730d7e48270769d5f83c67fc9f","tid":688600,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c663b808c7eef2ea99fcce502d086a35c37bb905","tid":688600,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"關sir好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6edf73fca11843ddaf4518331d12757a9bbceb1","tid":688600,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beafc497e6e8c2730d7e48270769d5f83c67fc9f","tid":688600,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"「我決定模仿偶像阿叻的打扮。我問煮飯婆，我有沒有三角小泳褲，她說：『啋！你平日游水都係着瞓覺嗰條孖煙囪0架啦！』於是我脫下長褲，穿上瞓覺嗰條孖煙囪。然後，借了煮飯婆的透明圍裙，圍在孖煙囪外面。<br />\n<br />\n「忽然省起，偶像阿叻，出鏡時，有時喜歡大熱天時穿皮草，於是又問煮飯婆，你有沒有皮草？她答，帶點怨氣：『你幾時買過皮草畀我？』我惟有把自己的棉襖穿上，很好，效果一樣戇居。然後用彩筆，在光頭上畫滿七色頭髮，像阿叻。煮飯婆問：「你去邊？」我答去行山。<br />\n<br />\n「穿着棉衲、透明圍裙和孖煙囪，『披着』一頭彩髮，我上到平日晨運之地。山上晨運客紛紛驚叫『怪物！』，爭相走避。我以一人之力，影響了一座山！<br />\n<br />\n「然後，我中暑暈倒。」<br />\n<br />\n下面有D難改喎"},{"pid":"3ca6e286d97bb7de61764cd072be9508c460a4f1","tid":688600,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"332eba8b298b1b7b50a060816dbc795ff5c4e1ff","tid":688600,"uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主五毛賈雨村抹黑本土派有功<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=211da708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1ad97502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bbe0f1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來大陸仔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132904_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132904_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=676cd829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/015141_926857a307104dcbbd5d1f1bf0ce191a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2F